    • HtmlTag

      public HtmlTag(String element, boolean isOpenTag)
      Constructs an HTML tag with the given element (like "table") and type. Self-closing tags like
      are considered to be "opening" tags, but return false from the requiresClosingTag method.
      参数:
      element - String the text inside the tag, such as title or head.
      isOpenTag - boolean a open tag is the tag without "/" in front of its element. Self-closing tags are considered open.
      抛出:
      NullPointerException - Throws a NullPointerException if element is null.

      public static LinkedList<HtmlTag> tokenize(String text)
